179890.name: Cumulative CO2 emissions from other industry
179890.description: Cumulative production-based emissions of carbon dioxide (CO2) from other industry sources since the first year of data availability, measured in tonnes. This is based on territorial emissions, which do not account for emissions embedded in traded goods.
